channel.title: SkyRune || The Ultimate Reality
channel.description:
[center][b]Introduction[/b] [i]Hello, my name is Jack. I'm known as [URL=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=560587]Skyro[/URL] on here. I've been around Runescape Private Servers for around about 3 years. I wouldn't say I'm the best coder, I'm not that great to be honest. This is going to be a massive learning curve for me and is going to help me to learn a lot about programming and a lot about the language of Java. I known for about 3 weeks, he is a cool guy and will be our website developer, we are making our project from a blank Emulous base with a twist. We're going to be re-writing every class and re-writing the game engine completely. We will be adding a better and different networking system but we're still deciding what to use.[/i][/center]
Please use this application to apply, we're looking for 2-3 more advanced developers.
